        <p>The path to the <MadCap:variable name="General.changelog" /> file location must be either absolute or relative. An example of an absolute path is: <tt>/usr/local/somefile.dat</tt> on Unix or <tt>c:\Directory\somefile.dat</tt> on Windows. </p>
        <p class="note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;Note: &lt;/b&gt;">Refer to <a href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/File.html">java.io.File javadoc</a> for the details of what to consider relative or absolute path.</p>
